    - target: {fileID: 2943576683157085486, guid: 054d47a25f1677047a0d604727bec216, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '- Chaser: 26 HP moves 3 spaces a turn, and can attack your base or
        friendly units if they are cardinally adjacent to it for 6 damage.


        -
        Ranged unit: 18 HP moves 2 spaces a turn and targets your player units. it
        can attack 5 tiles in all cardinal directions for 5 damage.


        -Healer:
        20HP can move 2 spaces a turn and targets damaged enemy units if it gets
        cardinally adjacent to a damaged unit it will heal them 4 HP a turn.


        -
        Base Eater: 40 HP only targets the base moves 1 space a turn and it will
        do 10 damage every turn it is cardinally adjacent to you base.


        -
        Warper: 23 HP moves 2 spaces a turn and can target 2 spaces in any cardinal
        direction. At the begining of the game it will create it''s own timeline
        and it will attack your friendly units and base in the timeline you are playing
        in for 5 damage. You can see it''s blue out line from your active timeline
        when the warper is in another timeline.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
